'''Uteens''' were an [[Eel/Legends|eel]]-like [[Species/Legends|species]] without [[Limb/Legends|hands]]. They were members of the [[New Republic/Legends|New Republic]].<ref name="CSWE">{{CSWECite|III|284|Uteen}}</ref>

{{Species-stub}}

==Behind the scenes==
Uteens first appeared in ''[[The New Rebellion]]'', a [[1996]] novel authored by [[Kristine Kathryn Rusch]].<ref name="TNR">''[[The New Rebellion]]''</ref>

